WEBVTT

01:30.970 --> 01:35.060
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.150 --> 01:35.680
Xiaolan.

01:35.680 --> 01:37.120
The Xiangsheng cuisine here
is very authentic.

01:35.789 --> 01:39.229
[2010]

01:37.150 --> 01:38.120
Try it out

01:38.120 --> 01:38.870
today.

01:39.070 --> 01:39.430
Okay.

01:41.479 --> 01:42.229
Mr. Chen?

01:43.400 --> 01:44.400
-Li.
-Hello, Mr. Chen.

01:44.400 --> 01:44.930
Xiaolan.

01:45.350 --> 01:46.680
You like spicy food too?

01:46.870 --> 01:48.070
I'm from Xiangsheng.

01:48.150 --> 01:49.280
Of course I love spicy food.

01:49.280 --> 01:49.680
I see.

01:49.840 --> 01:50.770
Enjoy your meal.

01:50.789 --> 01:51.120
Okay.

01:52.280 --> 01:52.810
Xiaolan!

01:53.229 --> 01:53.920
Come here.

01:53.950 --> 01:55.410
Let me have a word with you.

01:58.789 --> 01:59.870
With your education,

01:59.870 --> 02:00.760
it's your good fortune

02:00.760 --> 02:02.220
that you can get into Luna.

02:02.840 --> 02:04.700
You must work hard and learn well.

02:04.790 --> 02:06.790
These are the best years of your life.

02:06.790 --> 02:08.110
I have high hopes for you.

02:08.110 --> 02:09.120
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

02:09.120 --> 02:09.680
All right.

02:09.680 --> 02:10.750
Go and have your meal.

02:10.750 --> 02:11.080
Okay.

02:11.190 --> 02:12.150
Enjoy your meal.

02:15.870 --> 02:17.870
Hello, what would you like to order?

02:17.990 --> 02:20.700
[Episode 14: The Best Years]

02:22.560 --> 02:23.490
What's going on?

02:23.960 --> 02:26.220
Something has been off since yesterday.

02:27.030 --> 02:28.590
Maybe things

02:28.680 --> 02:30.010
happened too suddenly,

02:30.079 --> 02:31.140
and I got startled.

02:32.190 --> 02:33.560
You don't look like someone

02:33.560 --> 02:35.020
who gets startled easily.

02:37.400 --> 02:39.430
There's just been
too much going on lately.

02:39.430 --> 02:40.960
I'm probably just too tense and tired.

02:40.960 --> 02:41.360
This is a good opportunity

02:41.360 --> 02:42.560
to take a break.

02:42.960 --> 02:44.220
I'm glad you know that.

02:44.240 --> 02:45.630
Since you came to Shengcheng,

02:45.630 --> 02:48.030
you haven't had
a single day of proper rest.

02:55.190 --> 02:56.800
Shumai, barbecue pork bun.

02:57.710 --> 02:59.079
Barbecue pork bun.

02:59.310 --> 03:00.240
Do you want some?

03:00.710 --> 03:01.120
Yes.

03:04.190 --> 03:08.250
[Gangdao]

03:10.080 --> 03:10.520
Young Master.

03:10.520 --> 03:12.000
Your new teeth look nice.

03:13.800 --> 03:15.200
What are you laughing at?

03:16.960 --> 03:17.750
Is Xia Dajun

03:18.120 --> 03:19.320
still at the company?

03:19.400 --> 03:20.430
Xia Dajun?

03:21.190 --> 03:22.720
He's basically illiterate.

03:22.720 --> 03:23.720
He couldn't do

03:23.750 --> 03:24.870
anything right in the office.

03:24.870 --> 03:26.360
He was fired last month.

03:27.000 --> 03:28.079
That loser.

03:28.520 --> 03:30.630
He's even more useless than I imagined.

03:30.630 --> 03:31.630
How could Xia Xiaolan have

03:31.630 --> 03:32.690
a father like that?

03:34.360 --> 03:35.590
Get someone to keep an eye on him.

03:35.590 --> 03:37.910
Also find a chance to tell him

03:38.120 --> 03:40.560
that Xia Xiaolan is also in Shengcheng.

03:41.150 --> 03:42.630
Doesn't Miss Xia

03:42.630 --> 03:44.160
want nothing to do with him?

03:44.400 --> 03:45.960
That's why she needs to have something
to do with him.

03:45.960 --> 03:47.250
They are father and daughter, after all.

03:47.250 --> 03:48.980
You are so smart, Young Master.

03:51.079 --> 03:52.710
Can a family like that Jerk Zhou's

03:52.710 --> 03:53.560
accept Xia Xiaolan

03:53.560 --> 03:55.020
having a father like this?

04:00.360 --> 04:00.800
Hello?

04:02.560 --> 04:03.240
Daddy!

04:04.190 --> 04:04.710
Yes.

04:05.000 --> 04:06.030
I'm going to go discuss a contract.

04:06.030 --> 04:06.830
I'm very busy.

04:07.400 --> 04:09.760
Your second brother is busy with work,
and so are you.

04:09.760 --> 04:10.530
When will

04:10.560 --> 04:11.490
you two brothers

04:11.520 --> 04:13.680
sit down and have a meal with me

04:13.840 --> 04:14.910
to have a chat?

04:15.680 --> 04:16.610
Perfect timing.

04:16.950 --> 04:18.190
It's still early.

04:18.600 --> 04:20.190
Zhaoji should be at the company, right?

04:20.190 --> 04:22.320
I'll go pick him up to go home together.

04:27.920 --> 04:28.560
Change the route.

04:28.560 --> 04:29.360
Go to the Group.

04:29.360 --> 04:29.950
Okay.

04:39.730 --> 04:41.640
[Chengrong Group]

04:40.240 --> 04:40.920
Hello, Elder Young Master.

04:40.920 --> 04:42.450
Hello, Elder Young Master.

04:46.830 --> 04:48.430
The Second Young Master is in a meeting.

04:48.430 --> 04:49.680
Don't you recognize me?

04:49.680 --> 04:50.750
You are the Elder Young Master.

04:50.750 --> 04:51.830
I've seen your photo

04:51.830 --> 04:53.030
in the Group's files.

04:53.270 --> 04:54.930
And you still dare to block me?

04:55.950 --> 04:57.630
Where did Zhaoji find such a

04:57.680 --> 04:58.870
loyal,

04:59.680 --> 05:01.160
clueless Mainland girl?

05:04.120 --> 05:04.780
Xiaoqiong!

05:07.270 --> 05:07.870
Second Young Master.

05:07.870 --> 05:09.000
This is my big brother.

05:09.000 --> 05:10.190
We are all Du family members.

05:10.190 --> 05:12.390
Big Brother can come whenever he wants.

05:16.430 --> 05:17.500
Big Brother, your injury...

05:17.500 --> 05:19.480
The old man said
you're under a lot of pressure.

05:19.480 --> 05:21.480
He wanted me to pick you up from work.

05:21.800 --> 05:24.040
Your secretary is so fierce.

05:24.600 --> 05:25.950
You should just

05:26.690 --> 05:27.350
fire her.

05:31.000 --> 05:31.800
Just kidding.

05:32.070 --> 05:32.830
Relax.

05:34.000 --> 05:35.830
My car has been parked downstairs
for a while now.

05:35.830 --> 05:36.800
If we don't go down soon,

05:36.800 --> 05:38.330
the police will tow it away.

05:39.159 --> 05:40.290
I'll be right there.

05:46.720 --> 05:48.480
Come. A toast to the family.

05:51.560 --> 05:52.120
Dear.

05:58.360 --> 05:59.040
Zhaoji,

05:59.480 --> 06:00.480
you must remember,

06:00.480 --> 06:01.630
Work is work,

06:01.920 --> 06:03.260
but you must watch your health.

06:03.260 --> 06:05.410
Don't be a workaholic like your Daddy.

06:05.560 --> 06:06.290
Understand?

06:06.870 --> 06:07.680
I know, Mommy.

06:08.480 --> 06:09.010
Good boy.

06:09.310 --> 06:10.800
The Second Young Master works hard.

06:10.800 --> 06:12.270
But the Elder Young Master
must be working very hard

06:12.270 --> 06:13.510
to open up the market in the Mainland, right?

06:13.510 --> 06:14.910
Master, don't you agree?

06:15.800 --> 06:16.750
Working for the family

06:16.750 --> 06:18.010
isn't hard work at all.

06:18.070 --> 06:20.000
I test the waters in the Mainland,

06:20.310 --> 06:21.920
and he holds the fort here.

06:22.560 --> 06:24.240
We two brothers are working together

06:24.240 --> 06:26.000
to grow the company.

06:27.750 --> 06:29.210
Venturing out in the world

06:29.950 --> 06:31.410
can really toughen you up.

06:32.040 --> 06:33.170
Look at Zhaohui now.

06:34.270 --> 06:36.330
Zhaohui has become much more steady.

06:36.800 --> 06:37.530
That's good.

06:38.159 --> 06:39.090
I'm getting old.

06:39.870 --> 06:40.830
Chengrong

06:41.350 --> 06:43.350
will be handed over sooner or later.

06:48.630 --> 06:49.120
Daddy,

06:49.750 --> 06:50.490
the company right now

06:50.490 --> 06:52.350
cannot do without you at the helm.

06:52.480 --> 06:53.510
But you should

06:53.680 --> 06:55.210
reduce your workload a bit.

06:55.390 --> 06:57.190
I don't want you to get too tired.

06:57.240 --> 06:58.510
I wish you a long life

06:58.630 --> 06:59.600
and good health.

07:00.070 --> 07:00.830
Big Brother and I,

07:00.830 --> 07:01.940
along with our younger siblings,

07:01.940 --> 07:02.800
still have so much

07:02.800 --> 07:03.800
to learn from you.

07:07.310 --> 07:08.480
I won't let you down.

07:13.190 --> 07:13.850
Do you know?

07:16.230 --> 07:17.510
When I first came here,

07:19.310 --> 07:20.570
I started from scratch

07:21.720 --> 07:23.180
with absolutely nothing.

07:23.360 --> 07:24.920
I picked up

07:24.950 --> 07:26.750
small fish and shrimp by the pier,

07:26.750 --> 07:28.830
cured and boiled them,

07:28.830 --> 07:29.690
then sold them.

07:30.360 --> 07:32.800
Bit by bit, I earned my capital.

07:33.920 --> 07:35.600
It took me 40 years

07:36.360 --> 07:38.159
to build our Chengrong Group.

07:39.890 --> 07:40.970
I very much hope

07:41.000 --> 07:42.270
that 40 years from now,

07:43.070 --> 07:44.560
our Chengrong Group

07:45.270 --> 07:46.330
will still be here.

07:47.040 --> 07:48.750
I hope even more

07:49.600 --> 07:50.800
that the person in charge

07:50.800 --> 07:52.130
of Chengrong Group then

07:52.800 --> 07:53.800
will still be a Du.

07:58.360 --> 08:00.890
Of course,
it depends on everyone's ability.

08:00.980 --> 08:02.310
The most capable person

08:03.040 --> 08:06.190
will succeed me, Du Chengrong.

08:10.720 --> 08:11.780
Let's keep eating.

08:14.270 --> 08:14.830
Eat up.

08:14.930 --> 08:15.970
Carry on.

08:21.190 --> 08:22.160
What was the old man

08:22.160 --> 08:23.480
playing at just now?

08:24.160 --> 08:25.420
He only said half of it,

08:25.480 --> 08:26.810
acting all mysterious.

08:28.870 --> 08:29.510
Young Master,

08:29.510 --> 08:31.040
does your tooth still hurt?

08:31.360 --> 08:32.360
I've already made an appointment

08:32.360 --> 08:33.630
with Dr. Li.

08:34.789 --> 08:36.320
Tell him to wait for me at the hotel.

08:36.320 --> 08:37.450
I'll go tell him now.

08:48.750 --> 08:50.610
Are you seeing a doctor, Brother?

08:51.560 --> 08:52.720
I heard you had an accident

08:52.720 --> 08:53.580
in Shengcheng.

08:54.030 --> 08:55.790
I wanted to go there to see you.

08:55.910 --> 08:57.040
Why did you only plan

08:57.200 --> 08:58.130
but not act on it?

08:59.120 --> 09:00.080
Sorry, Brother.

09:00.440 --> 09:01.790
The Group kept me too busy.

09:01.790 --> 09:02.840
Forget it.

09:03.150 --> 09:04.120
Save that act

09:04.240 --> 09:05.480
to fool the old man.

09:05.960 --> 09:07.820
Teach your mom while you're at it.

09:07.870 --> 09:08.550
After dinner,

09:08.550 --> 09:10.480
the old man ran off to his new flame.

09:10.790 --> 09:11.990
You two are in danger.

09:13.370 --> 09:14.530
Don't assume that

09:15.030 --> 09:16.440
just because you hold a seat,

09:16.440 --> 09:18.370
you can call the shots in the Group.

09:22.630 --> 09:23.760
Since we were young,

09:24.480 --> 09:26.480
Daddy has always loved you the most.

09:26.870 --> 09:28.330
I've always been envious.

09:30.120 --> 09:31.450
I know you don't like me,

09:32.210 --> 09:33.120
thinking my mommy

09:33.120 --> 09:34.450
destroyed your family.

09:36.200 --> 09:37.240
But it's really difficult for us

09:37.240 --> 09:39.240
to understand the elders' affairs.

09:39.270 --> 09:40.120
If it weren't for my mommy,

09:40.120 --> 09:41.550
it would have been someone else.

09:41.550 --> 09:42.630
If you and I fight,

09:43.080 --> 09:43.870
others in the family

09:43.870 --> 09:45.270
will only clap and cheer.

09:46.150 --> 09:47.550
The Group is quite large.

09:48.510 --> 09:49.080
Brother,

09:49.150 --> 09:50.750
why don't we join forces?

09:51.030 --> 09:52.290
With brothers united,

09:52.510 --> 09:53.840
we can expand the Group.

09:58.480 --> 09:58.960
As expected

09:58.960 --> 10:00.890
of someone who has studied abroad!

10:01.240 --> 10:02.640
You're so knowledgeable

10:02.870 --> 10:04.270
and have a way with words.

10:04.600 --> 10:06.480
In this regard,
you're a hundred times better than me.

10:06.480 --> 10:07.340
Come on, drink.

10:11.440 --> 10:12.570
Rest well, Brother.

10:13.720 --> 10:15.270
I have other business at the company.

10:15.270 --> 10:16.270
I'll be going now.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.360
That Brat Ji.

10:24.080 --> 10:25.340
Who does he take after?

10:25.630 --> 10:27.560
The old man isn't like that either.

10:33.630 --> 10:34.480
Young Master.

10:36.360 --> 10:37.960
In this big house,

10:38.550 --> 10:40.270
it is better to be cautious

10:42.000 --> 10:43.600
with your words and actions.

10:43.790 --> 10:45.120
Do I need you to teach me?

10:46.360 --> 10:47.620
Where is Liu Tianquan?

10:47.720 --> 10:48.630
Tell him to come out.

10:48.630 --> 10:50.430
I have a score to settle with him.

10:50.840 --> 10:52.540
For what happened in Shengcheng?

10:52.540 --> 10:53.660
My brother told me.

10:54.000 --> 10:55.860
The reason he wanted to win the bid

10:56.030 --> 10:57.120
was just to help you out

10:57.120 --> 10:58.200
in Shengcheng.

11:00.200 --> 11:02.240
Do you think I'd believe you?

11:04.550 --> 11:06.720
It doesn't matter
if you believe it or not.

11:06.720 --> 11:07.870
Having a project to work on

11:07.870 --> 11:08.890
is better than letting the old man

11:08.890 --> 11:10.090
see this kind of news.

11:12.310 --> 11:13.640
[Chengrong's Eldest Young Master Fails to Woo Girl;
Love Turns to Hate as He Hits Someone with His Car]

11:16.480 --> 11:17.810
Well? Isn't she pretty?

11:18.340 --> 11:19.320
The one that the old man

11:19.320 --> 11:20.360
dances tango with—

11:20.360 --> 11:21.150
what was her name?

11:21.150 --> 11:21.840
Vivi?

11:22.200 --> 11:23.000
Is she pretty?

11:23.030 --> 11:24.360
She dances tango.

11:24.510 --> 11:25.570
Is she very pretty?

11:26.200 --> 11:27.440
She dances tango.

11:28.290 --> 11:29.550
All I know is jump rope.

12:06.120 --> 12:06.920
So beautiful.

12:14.520 --> 12:15.150
This is what Zhaohui

12:15.150 --> 12:16.600
takes from me the most.

12:17.150 --> 12:17.910
Always go

12:18.320 --> 12:20.360
for the prettiest girls.

12:22.660 --> 12:23.590
Don't you agree?

12:25.120 --> 12:26.360
With me,

12:26.740 --> 12:28.910
you are not allowed to
mention other women.

12:28.910 --> 12:29.840
I wouldn't dare.

12:41.840 --> 12:42.720
It just so happens a colleague of mine

12:42.720 --> 12:44.390
went on a business trip to Longcheng.

12:44.390 --> 12:44.790
Look,

12:45.200 --> 12:46.800
doesn't it look convincing?

12:49.750 --> 12:50.510
Zhou Cheng,

12:51.120 --> 12:52.220
this is the first time

12:52.220 --> 12:54.020
I've told such a big lie to my mom.

12:54.720 --> 12:56.200
I'm actually a bit nervous.

12:56.200 --> 12:57.440
What if she finds out?

12:58.360 --> 12:59.550
It's a white lie.

12:59.670 --> 13:00.870
Your mother will understand.

13:00.870 --> 13:01.720
Besides,

13:02.200 --> 13:04.130
she might not necessarily notice.

13:04.870 --> 13:06.120
What was so urgent?

13:06.240 --> 13:07.200
You didn't even have time

13:07.200 --> 13:08.550
to come back and get your clothes.

13:08.550 --> 13:09.390
Chen Xiliang suddenly

13:09.390 --> 13:11.080
called me and said

13:11.100 --> 13:13.100
something happened at the factory.

13:13.150 --> 13:14.390
Like the sky was falling.

13:14.390 --> 13:15.670
So I didn't have time to pack,

13:15.670 --> 13:16.670
and I just left.

13:17.390 --> 13:17.790
Right.

13:20.510 --> 13:21.710
What about your hand?

13:23.270 --> 13:24.800
What happened to your hand?

13:27.780 --> 13:29.980
I bumped into something at the factory.

13:30.120 --> 13:31.670
I wrapped it up to prevent infection.

13:31.670 --> 13:33.910
The doctor said
it'll be fine in a few days.

13:33.910 --> 13:35.000
I was quite worried too.

13:35.000 --> 13:35.600
So as soon as I got back,

13:35.600 --> 13:37.000
I took her to the hospital.

13:37.000 --> 13:38.120
The doctor said she's fine.

13:38.120 --> 13:39.180
I-I'm really fine.

13:39.390 --> 13:40.200
Fen.

13:40.730 --> 13:41.240
Granny Yu.

13:41.240 --> 13:42.080
I'm thirsty.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.540
Pour me some water.

13:51.630 --> 13:52.480
Granny Yu,

13:52.600 --> 13:53.510
thank you.

13:57.080 --> 13:59.210
She's lying to her own mum so it's fine.

13:59.910 --> 14:02.330
You're lying to your future mother-in-law.

14:02.330 --> 14:05.330
Aren't you afraid
she'll get back at you in the future?

14:05.510 --> 14:06.030
I...

14:06.130 --> 14:06.750
Granny Yu.

14:07.630 --> 14:08.960
Do you want roast goose?

14:11.270 --> 14:13.070
From the shop at the intersection.

14:13.070 --> 14:14.070
With crispy skin.

14:14.200 --> 14:15.000
-Okay.
-Okay.

14:16.670 --> 14:17.510
The one at the intersection.

14:17.510 --> 14:18.720
The skin has to be crispy.
Did you hear that?

14:18.720 --> 14:19.390
I heard that.

14:19.390 --> 14:19.990
You buy it.

14:20.200 --> 14:20.860
I'll buy it.

14:21.600 --> 14:22.720
Do you think

14:22.720 --> 14:24.780
Granny Yu will like this roast goose?

14:24.870 --> 14:25.810
How could she not?

14:25.810 --> 14:27.200
Isn't roast goose her favorite?

14:27.200 --> 14:27.670
Is it?

14:28.600 --> 14:30.130
She'll definitely like it.

14:35.360 --> 14:35.960
I'm sorry.

14:36.170 --> 14:37.500
I really didn't mean to.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.250
It's okay. Go ahead.

14:45.570 --> 14:46.200
Thank you, Miss.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.060
Goodbye, Miss.

14:47.120 --> 14:47.650
Goodbye.

14:54.480 --> 14:55.340
Do you know her?

14:56.720 --> 14:57.320
No.

14:58.360 --> 14:59.720
I just envy her.

15:00.440 --> 15:02.630
To be able to, in her best years,

15:02.790 --> 15:03.630
be carefree

15:03.840 --> 15:04.970
and laugh so freely.

15:07.150 --> 15:08.000
How do you know

15:08.030 --> 15:09.430
these are her best years?

15:10.210 --> 15:11.520
Maybe when she was 6,

15:11.550 --> 15:12.960
she was even more carefree.

15:12.960 --> 15:14.240
Or at 26,

15:14.360 --> 15:15.690
she might be even freer.

15:16.360 --> 15:17.240
You mean

15:17.610 --> 15:18.910
I'll have my best years too,

15:18.910 --> 15:19.440
right?

15:20.750 --> 15:21.720
I mean

15:22.200 --> 15:23.000
life is long—

15:23.600 --> 15:24.240
who knows

15:24.240 --> 15:25.440
when the best time is?

15:26.030 --> 15:27.630
To enjoy this moment,

15:28.080 --> 15:28.810
do your best,

15:29.030 --> 15:30.160
and leave no regrets

15:30.480 --> 15:32.140
would make it your best years.

15:32.870 --> 15:33.530
Zhou Cheng,

15:34.390 --> 15:35.850
are you enjoying yourself

15:35.870 --> 15:36.800
and happy enough

15:36.870 --> 15:37.730
at this moment?

15:39.750 --> 15:41.150
If I could be your family,

15:41.630 --> 15:43.090
that would be even better.

15:46.870 --> 15:48.130
With this roast goose,

15:48.550 --> 15:49.680
we'd be able to clear

15:49.870 --> 15:50.960
Granny Yu.

15:53.240 --> 15:53.840
By the way,

15:54.360 --> 15:55.270
I might need to go

15:55.270 --> 15:56.670
to Xiangcheng tomorrow.

15:56.870 --> 15:58.130
Will you be okay alone?

15:59.200 --> 15:59.720
Me?

16:00.880 --> 16:01.820
The guesthouse bid's results

16:01.820 --> 16:03.150
are out tomorrow, right?

16:03.150 --> 16:04.480
Did I remember wrongly?

16:04.840 --> 16:05.390
No, no.

16:05.720 --> 16:06.920
I just almost forgot.

16:07.200 --> 16:07.930
Don't worry.

16:08.300 --> 16:10.030
Second Uncle warned Du Zhaohui,

16:10.030 --> 16:11.790
and Du Zhaohui warned Liu Tianquan.

16:11.790 --> 16:12.270
I doubt they

16:12.270 --> 16:13.720
would dare to do anything.

16:13.720 --> 16:14.910
Let's go. Hurry inside.

16:14.910 --> 16:15.750
If we don't go in now,

16:15.750 --> 16:18.280
the roast goose skin
won't be crispy anymore.

16:20.090 --> 16:24.730
[Shengcheng Guesthouse Renovation Auction]

16:21.390 --> 16:23.450
So, that's settled for this project.

16:23.480 --> 16:25.610
Does anyone have any other questions?

16:25.910 --> 16:27.360
I'd like to ask—

16:27.630 --> 16:29.200
do you have something against

16:29.200 --> 16:30.330
Gangdao merchants?

16:30.750 --> 16:32.720
Since the project can be subcontracted,

16:32.720 --> 16:34.200
why are we the only ones

16:34.510 --> 16:35.520
being excluded?

16:36.390 --> 16:37.080
Comrade,

16:37.440 --> 16:38.970
we invited experts to vote.

16:39.320 --> 16:40.250
During the vote,

16:40.390 --> 16:41.320
we didn't disclose

16:41.320 --> 16:43.270
the bidding entity for each proposal.

16:43.270 --> 16:44.670
There couldn't be any bias.

16:44.670 --> 16:46.730
It was purely based on the proposals.

16:47.480 --> 16:48.810
Based on the proposals?

16:49.390 --> 16:50.240
With that

16:50.270 --> 16:52.000
tiny little company of theirs?

16:52.120 --> 16:53.120
They've only done

16:53.120 --> 16:54.600
interior decoration before.

16:54.600 --> 16:55.320
How could their proposal

16:55.320 --> 16:57.180
be better than ours at Chengrong?

16:59.120 --> 17:00.960
The proposal doesn't just need to be good;

17:00.960 --> 17:02.550
it also needs to be suitable.

17:02.550 --> 17:03.630
Chengrong Tianchen's proposal

17:03.630 --> 17:04.640
is too luxurious

17:05.030 --> 17:05.640
for us.

17:06.750 --> 17:07.609
As for Yuanhui,

17:08.240 --> 17:09.040
they provided

17:09.310 --> 17:11.240
the most suitable proposal for us.

17:11.550 --> 17:13.680
Although they are only renovating
two dining halls,

17:13.680 --> 17:15.410
but for the entire guesthouse,

17:15.480 --> 17:16.230
we also plan

17:16.829 --> 17:18.089
to use their proposal.

17:18.109 --> 17:19.109
What does that mean?

17:19.109 --> 17:21.240
We Shengyijian won the guest room bid,

17:21.400 --> 17:21.880
but we have to execute

17:21.880 --> 17:23.280
according to their plan?

17:23.349 --> 17:24.400
That's not appropriate, is it?

17:24.400 --> 17:24.829
Right.

17:26.440 --> 17:27.170
Comrade Xia,

17:27.550 --> 17:29.310
can you show your drawings

17:29.440 --> 17:31.100
to these gentlemen right now?

17:31.200 --> 17:32.460
Of course, no problem.

17:32.640 --> 17:33.720
I'd be happy to let this gentleman

17:33.720 --> 17:34.790
who didn't win the bid

17:34.790 --> 17:36.790
accept his defeat wholeheartedly.

17:37.400 --> 17:37.830
Uncle.

17:39.680 --> 17:40.110
Here.

17:43.880 --> 17:44.340
Thanks.

17:45.110 --> 17:45.770
Here you go.

17:46.240 --> 17:46.900
Take a look.

17:49.440 --> 17:50.590
Look at this design.

17:51.000 --> 17:52.330
It's indeed quite good.

17:54.310 --> 17:55.160
Take a look at this one too.

17:55.160 --> 17:56.000
Haven't seen these before.

17:56.000 --> 17:56.400
Right.

17:57.200 --> 17:58.460
Since that's the case,

17:58.640 --> 17:59.830
let them handle it.

18:01.240 --> 18:02.350
But regarding the details,

18:02.350 --> 18:03.000
we still need to

18:03.000 --> 18:03.810
communicate with Yuanhui's designers

18:03.810 --> 18:04.570
further.

18:04.920 --> 18:05.270
Okay.

18:05.720 --> 18:07.120
This proposal is not bad.

18:07.550 --> 18:08.450
This design

18:08.480 --> 18:09.480
is very original.

18:09.680 --> 18:10.010
Look.

18:10.070 --> 18:11.480
I've never seen anything like it.

18:11.480 --> 18:13.160
It brings out the full effect.

18:16.270 --> 18:17.550
This is a design drawing?

18:17.550 --> 18:18.030
Yes.

18:18.400 --> 18:20.530
You haven't seen one before, have you?

18:38.510 --> 18:39.200
Ms. Xia.

18:39.640 --> 18:40.700
Congratulations.

18:41.040 --> 18:42.240
I heard this is Yuanhui's first ever bid

18:42.240 --> 18:44.070
and you won it.

18:44.590 --> 18:45.790
That calls for a celebration.

18:45.790 --> 18:46.480
Mr. Du,

18:46.960 --> 18:49.020
although Yuanhui is a small company,

18:49.160 --> 18:50.130
I'm confident

18:50.160 --> 18:51.560
it's as good as any other.

18:52.200 --> 18:53.960
Chengrong might dominate Gangdao,

18:53.960 --> 18:55.590
but it might not suit the mainland.

18:55.590 --> 18:56.480
In this bid,

18:56.680 --> 18:58.280
Chengrong was pretty lousy.

18:58.750 --> 19:01.080
But because of your interference, Mr. Du,

19:01.370 --> 19:02.520
it made Mr. Liu

19:02.960 --> 19:04.420
think they went easy on us.

19:05.480 --> 19:06.240
Xia Xiaolan.

19:06.550 --> 19:07.640
That's enough.

19:09.150 --> 19:11.210
Ms. Xia is still as straightforward.

19:11.270 --> 19:11.930
I like that.

19:12.680 --> 19:13.790
But I came here today

19:13.790 --> 19:14.920
for something else.

19:15.730 --> 19:17.410
The lawyers have settled

19:17.440 --> 19:18.720
Kang Wei's compensation.

19:18.720 --> 19:21.200
As for Mr. Liu's car,

19:21.880 --> 19:23.560
I've made an appointment
with the dealership.

19:23.560 --> 19:24.830
Are you interested in coming with me

19:24.830 --> 19:26.030
to take a look?

19:26.480 --> 19:28.180
The car is being compensated to me.

19:28.180 --> 19:29.400
Why would Xiaolan go?

19:29.960 --> 19:31.030
If Mr. Liu wants to go,

19:31.030 --> 19:31.980
you can come along too.

19:31.980 --> 19:32.450
No need.

19:32.640 --> 19:33.830
Just replace it with the same model.

19:33.830 --> 19:35.360
That car was already so old.

19:35.550 --> 19:36.680
Wait a moment, wait.

19:39.350 --> 19:40.750
Why not choose a new one?

19:42.440 --> 19:42.970
Let's go.

19:43.280 --> 19:44.240
I'll buy you a different model.

19:44.240 --> 19:44.900
How's that?

19:53.460 --> 19:54.920
Don't be so polite with me.

19:55.860 --> 19:57.010
Sis Bai, I've caused you trouble

19:57.010 --> 19:58.210
these few days.

19:58.780 --> 20:00.120
Let's go get some Japanese food.

20:00.120 --> 20:00.830
Cheng took me

20:00.830 --> 20:02.030
to eat it in Jingcheng before.

20:02.030 --> 20:03.160
I heard one opened in Shengcheng too.

20:03.160 --> 20:04.020
Let's go try it.

20:04.110 --> 20:05.480
You're still thinking about eating?

20:05.480 --> 20:06.310
My shop hasn't been properly managed

20:06.310 --> 20:07.510
these few days.

20:07.840 --> 20:09.700
Still thinking about eating out?

20:09.790 --> 20:11.000
You are right.

20:11.030 --> 20:12.360
Let's make money first.

20:12.590 --> 20:14.250
We'll eat after we make money.

20:15.750 --> 20:16.750
Which arm did you injure?

20:16.750 --> 20:17.280
This one.

20:18.450 --> 20:18.960
Don't, don't!

20:18.960 --> 20:20.560
It just healed, just healed.

20:22.160 --> 20:22.680
Mom.

20:22.920 --> 20:23.520
Mrs. Kang.

20:24.260 --> 20:25.400
Where is Second Uncle?

20:25.400 --> 20:27.400
He went to the entrance to hail a cab.

20:27.510 --> 20:28.440
Ms. Zhenzhu.

20:28.680 --> 20:30.510
Let's have dinner together tonight.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.750
No need to trouble yourselves—

20:31.750 --> 20:32.400
Sis Bai.

20:33.070 --> 20:35.240
I've just survived a disaster.

20:35.270 --> 20:36.310
You have to go

20:36.330 --> 20:36.830
to join in

20:36.830 --> 20:37.440
the fun

20:37.510 --> 20:38.090
and wash away the bad luck.

20:38.090 --> 20:39.220
Invite Xiaolan too.

20:39.240 --> 20:40.500
Let's all go together.

20:40.840 --> 20:42.000
Then I'll trouble you, Ma'am.

20:42.000 --> 20:42.570
Hurry, hurry.

20:42.570 --> 20:43.750
-Let's go.
-Not at all.

20:43.750 --> 20:44.840
Let's eat. Let's eat.

20:44.840 --> 20:45.590
I'll carry it. I'll carry it.

20:45.590 --> 20:46.200
Let's go.

20:46.220 --> 20:46.950
I'll take it!

20:47.750 --> 20:48.160
Hey—

20:48.480 --> 20:49.610
You've got them all?

21:03.680 --> 21:04.480
Second Uncle.

21:04.920 --> 21:05.680
Let's go eat.

21:05.960 --> 21:06.750
Don't make Sis Bai

21:06.750 --> 21:07.610
and my mom wait.

21:09.510 --> 21:09.960
Come.

21:10.590 --> 21:11.850
Pull up a stool and sit.

21:12.030 --> 21:12.690
Let's chat.

21:13.160 --> 21:14.070
Second Uncle.

21:15.640 --> 21:16.170
Sit down.

21:26.180 --> 21:26.960
Sit, Zhenzhu, sit.

21:26.960 --> 21:27.400
Okay.

21:29.200 --> 21:30.110
Have some tea.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.240
Okay, thanks.

21:33.990 --> 21:34.520
Zhenzhu.

21:34.680 --> 21:35.880
I'll do it. I'll do it.

21:35.880 --> 21:37.030
Your arm just healed.

21:37.030 --> 21:38.030
I'll do it myself.

21:38.640 --> 21:39.240
Thank you.

21:41.440 --> 21:43.270
Are you a Shengcheng local?

21:43.680 --> 21:45.200
I'm from Longcheng.

21:46.830 --> 21:48.750
My family
used to run a martial arts school.

21:48.750 --> 21:49.790
After the school closed down,

21:49.790 --> 21:51.310
I came out to do business.

21:51.920 --> 21:52.970
Xiaolan told me

21:53.000 --> 21:53.880
that there'd be more opportunities

21:53.880 --> 21:55.010
here in Shengcheng,

21:55.240 --> 21:56.310
so I came here.

21:58.350 --> 21:59.920
So, is your family all here?

22:01.890 --> 22:03.210
It's just my grandma

22:03.240 --> 22:04.440
and me now.

22:04.790 --> 22:05.860
Grandma is old,

22:05.920 --> 22:07.520
so I have to bring her with me.

22:09.170 --> 22:10.810
You've had it tough, girl.

22:12.790 --> 22:14.190
What is your zodiac sign?

22:14.720 --> 22:16.510
I heard Wei call you Sis Bai.

22:16.680 --> 22:17.940
Are you older than him?

22:20.120 --> 22:21.890
I'm the same age as Wei.

22:21.920 --> 22:23.590
He probably calls me Sis

22:24.000 --> 22:25.530
because I'm a good fighter?

22:26.240 --> 22:27.680
He calls Xiaolan Sis too,

22:27.930 --> 22:28.830
even though Xiaolan is actually

22:28.830 --> 22:30.160
a year younger than him.

22:39.350 --> 22:40.150
Have some tea.

22:40.160 --> 22:41.620
Please, have some tea too.

22:44.030 --> 22:45.160
I'll go check why Xiaolan

22:45.160 --> 22:46.070
isn't here yet.

22:47.110 --> 22:48.000
Slow down.

22:50.270 --> 22:51.200
Look at this kid.

22:51.510 --> 22:52.590
She's shy.

22:54.000 --> 22:54.800
Second Uncle,

22:55.160 --> 22:55.980
doing business

22:55.980 --> 22:57.130
isn't that easy.

22:57.160 --> 22:58.290
Since it's not easy,

22:58.350 --> 22:59.680
go back to your job.

23:00.270 --> 23:01.130
I won't go back.

23:01.730 --> 23:02.450
If I go back,

23:02.480 --> 23:03.110
for the rest of my life,

23:03.110 --> 23:04.270
I'll have to listen to you.

23:04.270 --> 23:04.880
Whatever you say,

23:04.880 --> 23:05.880
I'll have to do it.

23:05.880 --> 23:06.550
Whatever we say

23:06.550 --> 23:07.750
is for your own good.

23:08.160 --> 23:09.160
Would we harm you?

23:09.640 --> 23:11.750
I know you wouldn't harm me.

23:12.030 --> 23:12.790
But you would turn me

23:12.790 --> 23:13.960
into a loser.

23:14.960 --> 23:16.090
What are you saying?

23:16.590 --> 23:17.310
Second Uncle,

23:17.310 --> 23:19.110
I used to think you didn't train me

23:19.110 --> 23:20.000
or value me.

23:20.440 --> 23:21.510
But while I was in the hospital,

23:21.510 --> 23:23.380
I realized you really care about me.

23:23.380 --> 23:24.750
Maybe you feel bad

23:24.830 --> 23:26.270
that I lost my dad when I was young,

23:26.270 --> 23:28.070
so you didn't want to be harsh on me.

23:28.070 --> 23:29.110
You wanted me to have an easy

23:29.110 --> 23:30.370
and comfortable life.

23:30.750 --> 23:32.030
But no one has it easy.

23:32.310 --> 23:33.170
Look at Sis Bai.

23:33.310 --> 23:34.830
When she first came to Longcheng,

23:34.830 --> 23:36.360
she was just a fruit seller.

23:36.480 --> 23:38.550
She worked for 5 years
before she could open a shop.

23:38.550 --> 23:39.520
Xiaolan, too.

23:39.720 --> 23:41.340
She used to sell duck eggs in Anqing.

23:41.340 --> 23:43.250
She made it here dime by dime.

23:43.640 --> 23:44.510
Cheng.

23:44.750 --> 23:46.550
He's a top student from Huaqing,

23:46.590 --> 23:48.210
but he started out
by doing odd jobs at a law firm.

23:48.210 --> 23:49.110
None of them had it easy.

23:49.110 --> 23:50.440
But they didn't give up.

23:50.590 --> 23:52.240
Can you compare yourself to them?

23:52.240 --> 23:53.760
They have drive and grit.

23:53.790 --> 23:55.050
Do you have the brains?

23:55.960 --> 23:56.480
Do you?

23:57.750 --> 23:58.440
Talk!

23:59.550 --> 24:00.160
Yes.

24:00.480 --> 24:01.110
I don't.

24:01.360 --> 24:02.250
I'm not as smart

24:02.550 --> 24:04.010
or as hardworking as them.

24:07.920 --> 24:08.480
But...

24:08.670 --> 24:09.930
But I can change.

24:09.960 --> 24:11.110
I can learn.

24:11.550 --> 24:12.510
In the past, you guys

24:12.510 --> 24:13.710
always protected me.

24:13.750 --> 24:14.680
Now I just want

24:14.790 --> 24:16.120
to venture out on my own.

24:16.270 --> 24:17.670
It is harder than before,

24:17.750 --> 24:19.160
but I'm happier too.

24:19.270 --> 24:20.310
Even if I earn 10 yuan,

24:20.310 --> 24:21.550
I can be happy all day.

24:23.400 --> 24:24.440
Anyway, I don't care.

24:24.440 --> 24:25.790
I'm staying in Shengcheng.

24:25.790 --> 24:26.990
I won't be a deserter.

24:39.000 --> 24:39.790
Hello, Mrs. Kang.

24:39.790 --> 24:41.050
You're here, Xiaolan.

24:41.240 --> 24:41.750
Zhenzhu.

24:41.750 --> 24:42.610
Come, sit here.

24:42.880 --> 24:43.440
I...

24:43.590 --> 24:44.000
Come on.

24:44.000 --> 24:44.800
Sit down. Sit.

24:45.200 --> 24:45.640
Sit.

24:46.030 --> 24:46.440
Okay.

24:49.550 --> 24:50.150
Mrs. Kang,

24:50.790 --> 24:52.790
Zhenzhu has something to say to you.

24:53.160 --> 24:54.590
It's about her and Wei.

24:56.510 --> 24:57.070
Go ahead.

24:58.350 --> 24:58.950
Mrs. Kang,

24:59.420 --> 25:00.880
although I don't really understand

25:00.880 --> 25:02.140
these kinds of things,

25:02.270 --> 25:02.880
I think

25:02.880 --> 25:04.540
you must have misunderstood.

25:04.550 --> 25:05.550
Wei and I

25:05.750 --> 25:07.000
are friends.

25:07.830 --> 25:09.720
We are business partners.

25:10.310 --> 25:11.790
We have a good relationship, but...

25:11.790 --> 25:12.240
it's not

25:12.240 --> 25:13.510
what you think.

25:20.680 --> 25:21.270
Sorry!

25:27.790 --> 25:28.960
You child...

25:29.790 --> 25:31.030
You are quite direct.

25:32.680 --> 25:33.350
Okay.

25:34.030 --> 25:35.720
Since you've put it that way,

25:36.680 --> 25:38.000
I understand now.

25:39.070 --> 25:40.070
Come on, sit down.

25:40.350 --> 25:41.200
Mom.

25:42.680 --> 25:43.810
What do you know now?

25:45.000 --> 25:45.830
I know that you are still

25:45.830 --> 25:47.000
a disappointment.

25:50.650 --> 25:51.350
-Hello, Mr. Kang.
-Hello, Mr. Kang.

25:51.350 --> 25:51.750
Hello.

25:51.880 --> 25:52.410
Sit, sit.

25:55.830 --> 25:56.200
Sit.

26:00.110 --> 26:00.510
Come.

26:03.310 --> 26:04.710
This first glass of wine,

26:05.070 --> 26:06.830
I'd like to toast
to all our young friends here

26:06.830 --> 26:08.100
for taking care of

26:08.240 --> 26:09.840
Kang Wei these past few days.

26:10.160 --> 26:10.590
Come.

26:15.160 --> 26:16.220
This second glass,

26:16.480 --> 26:18.590
I'd like to toast
to Ms. Bai Zhenzhu.

26:20.440 --> 26:22.480
Thank you for kicking Du Zhaohui.

26:24.030 --> 26:25.230
No need to be nervous.

26:25.970 --> 26:27.110
You did what everyone wanted to do

26:27.110 --> 26:28.110
but was afraid to.

26:28.720 --> 26:30.310
Thank you
for treating Kang Wei as a friend

26:30.310 --> 26:31.640
and standing up for him.

26:32.350 --> 26:33.350
It was impulsive,

26:33.960 --> 26:36.310
but also it was also
out of loyalty and righteousness.

26:36.310 --> 26:37.110
Rest assured.

26:37.960 --> 26:39.000
If the Du family

26:39.310 --> 26:40.570
gives you any trouble,

26:41.110 --> 26:43.370
the Kang family
will take full responsibility.

26:43.370 --> 26:44.570
This glass is for you.

26:44.790 --> 26:47.050
Sorry for causing you trouble, Mr. Kang.

26:47.960 --> 26:48.400
Sit.

26:50.750 --> 26:51.750
Don't be nervous.

26:52.160 --> 26:54.220
I'm just Kang Wei's parent right now.

26:54.400 --> 26:56.200
It's only right that I thank you.

26:56.680 --> 26:58.210
As for whether you should be

26:58.550 --> 26:59.880
that impulsive in the future,

26:59.880 --> 27:01.790
and how to control your impulses,

27:02.400 --> 27:03.240
you should really

27:03.240 --> 27:04.300
learn a thing or two

27:04.420 --> 27:05.640
from your good friend here,

27:05.640 --> 27:06.880
Xia Xiaolan.

27:07.070 --> 27:08.200
Thank you, Mr. Kang.

27:09.120 --> 27:10.680
Whether Kang Wei makes money in the south

27:10.680 --> 27:11.480
is secondary.

27:12.240 --> 27:13.440
The most important thing is that

27:13.440 --> 27:15.570
he has made such good friends like you.

27:17.550 --> 27:19.480
Your trip to Shengcheng this time,

27:19.590 --> 27:20.200
Kang Wei,

27:20.750 --> 27:21.810
was worth the trip.

27:23.720 --> 27:24.520
Second Uncle.

27:24.800 --> 27:26.530
You're agreeing to let me stay?

27:31.590 --> 27:32.050
Come on.

27:32.430 --> 27:33.160
Let's eat.

27:35.300 --> 27:36.700
Second Uncle, you first.

27:39.410 --> 27:40.860
Second Uncle, eat up.

27:43.010 --> 27:46.640
[Winter, 1989]

27:55.000 --> 27:55.440
Hello!

27:56.640 --> 27:57.370
As you asked,

27:57.550 --> 27:58.680
I got you a new one.

27:59.000 --> 28:00.460
The paperwork is all done.

28:00.680 --> 28:01.310
Ms. Xia.

28:01.590 --> 28:03.400
Your car is too ugly.

28:03.720 --> 28:04.780
Why don't I buy a new

28:04.880 --> 28:06.080
and nicer one for you?

28:06.640 --> 28:07.070
My uncle

28:07.070 --> 28:08.590
is supervising work
at Shengcheng Guesthouse.

28:08.590 --> 28:09.650
Send it over there.

28:10.550 --> 28:11.680
Drive it to Shengcheng Guesthouse.

28:11.680 --> 28:12.070
Go on.

28:12.510 --> 28:13.310
Where are you going?

28:13.310 --> 28:14.070
I'll give you a ride.

28:14.070 --> 28:14.590
It's faster.

28:14.590 --> 28:15.790
Get in my car. Come on.

28:16.790 --> 28:17.440
What are you doing?

28:17.440 --> 28:17.960
What are you doing?

28:17.960 --> 28:18.620
Who are you?

28:18.790 --> 28:19.400
What's your problem?

28:19.400 --> 28:20.070
Let go!

28:25.790 --> 28:26.320
Xiaolan.

28:26.720 --> 28:27.580
This is Ge Jian.

28:27.720 --> 28:29.590
He was also a disciple
at Bai Martial Arts School.

28:29.590 --> 28:30.270
When you go out,

28:30.270 --> 28:31.790
you need a driver and a bodyguard.

28:31.790 --> 28:32.350
Since I'm going on
a business trip this time,

28:32.350 --> 28:33.410
I brought him over.

28:34.000 --> 28:34.930
How thoughtful.

28:35.590 --> 28:36.160
Ge Jian.

28:36.590 --> 28:38.440
Today is your first day.

28:38.630 --> 28:39.760
Your first job is

28:39.790 --> 28:41.240
to make this man in purple

28:41.240 --> 28:42.240
stay away from me.

28:42.360 --> 28:43.030
And him too.

28:44.160 --> 28:44.960
Okay, Ms. Xia.

28:45.310 --> 28:45.840
Let's go.

28:46.330 --> 28:47.930
Where are you going, Ms. Xia?

28:48.590 --> 28:49.450
Ge Jian, right?

28:49.640 --> 28:50.700
I'll remember you!

28:51.440 --> 28:51.880
Get in.

28:51.880 --> 28:52.400
Ge Jian!

28:52.480 --> 28:54.280
I'll remember you too, Ge Jian!

28:55.070 --> 28:56.890
Come to Gangdao if you have the guts.

28:56.890 --> 28:57.830
Think you're tough because you're big?

28:57.830 --> 28:59.360
It's just useless muscles.

28:59.920 --> 29:01.320
Here. Careful, it's hot.

29:06.960 --> 29:07.920
Second Uncle agreed

29:07.920 --> 29:09.110
to let Kang Wei stay

29:09.640 --> 29:11.170
because he wants to push us.

29:11.510 --> 29:12.640
Although each of us

29:12.640 --> 29:13.830
has a business to run,

29:13.830 --> 29:15.160
none of them are on a large scale.

29:15.160 --> 29:16.900
There are opportunities
everywhere in Shengcheng,

29:16.900 --> 29:18.490
but few have made it big.

29:19.920 --> 29:20.480
Xiaolan.

29:21.030 --> 29:21.590
Since you say that,

29:21.590 --> 29:22.650
do you have an idea?

29:23.240 --> 29:24.790
Uncle has now secured

29:25.070 --> 29:26.840
the renovation
of the guesthouse restaurant.

29:26.840 --> 29:27.590
As for building materials,

29:27.590 --> 29:29.070
we can get them from Zhenzhu.

29:29.070 --> 29:30.440
The projects we handle in the future

29:30.440 --> 29:31.640
will only get bigger.

29:31.680 --> 29:32.510
The shop right now

29:32.510 --> 29:33.510
isn't big enough?

29:33.790 --> 29:34.480
It's small.

29:34.640 --> 29:35.770
And anyone can do it.

29:35.790 --> 29:37.050
There's no advantage.

29:37.550 --> 29:38.350
I think

29:38.590 --> 29:40.650
we can build a building materials center.

29:40.650 --> 29:42.110
In the future,
whether it's residential housing

29:42.110 --> 29:43.270
or commercial renovation,

29:43.270 --> 29:44.350
whenever someone mentions
building materials,

29:44.350 --> 29:45.110
the first thing they'll think of

29:45.110 --> 29:45.790
is us.

29:45.830 --> 29:47.630
As Shengcheng develops faster,

29:47.790 --> 29:49.720
where there's a market, there's demand.

29:49.720 --> 29:50.920
Instead of waiting for others

29:50.920 --> 29:51.640
to take this business,

29:51.640 --> 29:52.160
we should

29:52.160 --> 29:54.000
seize the opportunity ourselves.

29:54.000 --> 29:54.440
Okay.

29:54.960 --> 29:56.750
I'll discuss it with Sis Bai

29:56.880 --> 29:58.140
and come up with a plan.

29:58.730 --> 30:00.070
You know how to make plans now,

30:00.070 --> 30:00.640
Wei?

30:00.880 --> 30:02.200
You're amazing.

30:07.400 --> 30:08.060
Zhou Cheng.

30:10.480 --> 30:11.940
Did you try the meatballs?

30:12.440 --> 30:13.040
Yes, I did.

30:14.240 --> 30:15.440
It's the best time for

30:15.440 --> 30:17.100
mutton hotpot when it's cold.

30:17.210 --> 30:18.000
But I feel like

30:18.000 --> 30:19.070
the mutton here

30:19.130 --> 30:19.790
isn't as authentic as

30:19.790 --> 30:21.510
what we had in the capital.

30:22.750 --> 30:23.880
By the way, Cheng Zi,

30:23.880 --> 30:26.000
your trip to Jingcheng this time...

30:32.670 --> 30:34.200
You went back to Jingcheng?

30:42.030 --> 30:42.590
Xiaolan.

30:43.720 --> 30:45.920
It was a sudden trip,

30:46.160 --> 30:47.310
so I didn't tell you.

30:48.640 --> 30:49.240
I'm sorry.

30:50.070 --> 30:50.680
It's fine.

30:51.270 --> 30:52.400
We're all busy.

30:52.730 --> 30:54.070
Forgetting things occasionally

30:54.070 --> 30:54.680
is normal.

30:57.270 --> 30:58.920
How is work lately?

30:59.070 --> 31:00.000
Is it going well?

31:00.400 --> 31:01.330
It's going well.

31:01.790 --> 31:03.450
I've started handling cases.

31:03.830 --> 31:05.030
It's quite fulfilling.

31:05.030 --> 31:07.160
It's just that some things are tricky,

31:07.200 --> 31:08.930
and haven't been resolved yet.

31:12.000 --> 31:12.800
What's wrong?

31:13.550 --> 31:14.240
Nothing.

31:14.480 --> 31:15.810
It's almost New Year's.

31:16.510 --> 31:17.030
Yeah.

31:17.790 --> 31:19.120
It's almost New Year's.

31:28.030 --> 31:29.230
I'm heading back now.

31:29.920 --> 31:30.450
Bye-bye.

31:30.590 --> 31:31.120
Bye-bye.

32:08.000 --> 32:08.920
Wei,

32:08.920 --> 32:10.250
you really act fast now.

32:10.550 --> 32:12.010
You're planning already?

32:12.350 --> 32:14.280
I was all geared up to plan,

32:14.310 --> 32:16.370
then got discouraged and shelved it.

32:17.880 --> 32:18.740
What happened?

32:18.750 --> 32:19.270
Look.

32:20.400 --> 32:21.930
Sis Bai and I calculated it.

32:22.480 --> 32:23.350
For a shop,

32:23.530 --> 32:25.130
the renovation and rent

32:25.160 --> 32:26.320
aren't the biggest expenses.

32:26.320 --> 32:27.240
The main thing is,

32:27.240 --> 32:29.160
for the scale Xiaolan mentioned,

32:29.420 --> 32:30.890
it requires a lot of

32:30.910 --> 32:32.370
upfront inventory costs;

32:32.640 --> 32:34.200
only then can you stock the shop

32:34.200 --> 32:34.800
properly.

32:35.680 --> 32:36.920
A rough estimate shows

32:36.920 --> 32:39.180
we need at least 300,000 yuan in capital.

32:40.030 --> 32:40.590
Cheng,

32:41.250 --> 32:43.180
how much is your salary this month?

32:44.160 --> 32:45.110
It's about 300.

32:46.200 --> 32:47.680
Do you know

32:47.770 --> 32:48.790
how much profit

32:48.880 --> 32:50.480
Sis Bai and my stall make now?

32:51.270 --> 32:52.240
Less than 3,000.

32:52.400 --> 32:53.000
Tell me,

32:53.200 --> 32:55.130
how long will it take to get enough?

32:55.440 --> 32:56.440
3,000?

32:58.350 --> 32:59.750
Self-employed people really make more.

32:59.750 --> 33:00.590
But those profits

33:00.590 --> 33:02.000
don't go into our pockets.

33:02.000 --> 33:02.920
They are all reinvested

33:02.920 --> 33:04.250
to expand the business.

33:05.160 --> 33:07.750
The goal is ambitious,

33:08.030 --> 33:09.880
but the path is winding.

33:10.110 --> 33:11.110
Right now,

33:11.440 --> 33:12.830
I just need to work hard,

33:13.160 --> 33:14.160
fight hard,

33:14.310 --> 33:15.970
and make something of myself!

33:17.350 --> 33:17.950
All right.

33:18.200 --> 33:19.420
Then go make something of yourself

33:19.420 --> 33:20.110
and show me.

33:20.880 --> 33:21.550
You bet!

33:24.960 --> 33:26.920
Chen, this isn't like you.

33:27.110 --> 33:28.710
Have you asked the magazine?

33:29.120 --> 33:30.310
If you have any problems using it,

33:30.310 --> 33:31.240
feel free to contact me anytime.

33:31.240 --> 33:32.170
Okay, thank you.

33:32.270 --> 33:33.130
Appreciate it.

33:33.510 --> 33:34.910
How about the TV station?

33:36.790 --> 33:37.440
Granny Yu.

33:38.110 --> 33:39.720
The phone was just installed,

33:39.720 --> 33:41.850
and she's already doing business calls?

33:41.850 --> 33:42.720
Xiaolan said

33:42.750 --> 33:44.020
she has to earn back the installation fee

33:44.020 --> 33:45.230
as soon as possible.

33:45.400 --> 33:45.960
Really?

33:46.000 --> 33:46.800
Impressive.

33:47.880 --> 33:48.480
Granny Yu.

33:48.640 --> 33:50.270
I made

33:50.480 --> 33:51.890
fig and spare rib soup.

33:52.000 --> 33:53.030
Could you go check on it for me?

33:53.030 --> 33:53.480
Okay.

33:54.240 --> 33:55.040
I'll go check.

33:57.960 --> 33:58.400
No,

33:58.880 --> 34:00.920
you can't just give up like this.

34:01.110 --> 34:02.110
If this works,

34:02.310 --> 34:03.400
Luna will succeed.

34:04.030 --> 34:04.590
Xiaolan,

34:04.920 --> 34:06.590
I've gone through all the friends

34:06.590 --> 34:07.400
and connections

34:07.400 --> 34:08.510
that I can find.

34:08.800 --> 34:10.969
I really don't have any contacts
for the Chinese New Year Gala.

34:10.969 --> 34:11.960
If you don't have connections,

34:11.960 --> 34:13.510
then create them.

34:13.840 --> 34:15.510
If we can't get into
their costume department,

34:15.510 --> 34:17.150
there are other departments too.

34:17.150 --> 34:18.000
If all else fails,

34:18.000 --> 34:19.710
they must need people
to help hand out box lunches, right?

34:19.710 --> 34:20.900
As long as you can get in,

34:20.900 --> 34:22.320
you'll meet more people.

34:22.630 --> 34:24.190
With your smarts,

34:24.360 --> 34:25.960
it won't be hard to find a way.

34:26.190 --> 34:27.320
Don't worry.

34:27.480 --> 34:28.739
I'm asking around too.

34:28.760 --> 34:30.880
We're fighting side by side now.

34:31.070 --> 34:32.969
I'll let you know as soon as I have news.

34:32.969 --> 34:33.760
I believe

34:33.850 --> 34:34.920
that until the very last moment,

34:34.920 --> 34:35.960
you won't give up.

34:36.070 --> 34:36.510
Right?

34:37.800 --> 34:39.199
Since you put it that way,

34:39.630 --> 34:40.230
all right,

34:40.590 --> 34:41.449
I won't give up.

34:42.230 --> 34:43.510
I've bought the plane ticket.

34:43.510 --> 34:44.920
I'll arrive in Jingcheng tonight.

34:44.920 --> 34:45.320
Okay.

34:45.630 --> 34:47.360
You'll surely be busy on New Year's Eve.

34:47.360 --> 34:48.510
So I'll wish you

34:48.550 --> 34:49.710
a Happy New Year in advance.

34:49.710 --> 34:50.570
Happy New Year.

34:51.000 --> 34:51.600
Good luck.

35:06.670 --> 35:08.030
My goodness.

35:08.770 --> 35:10.110
We're going back for the New Year,

35:10.110 --> 35:10.840
not moving house.

35:10.840 --> 35:12.230
Why are you bringing so much stuff?

35:12.230 --> 35:14.160
It doesn't hurt to bring a bit more.

35:14.520 --> 35:15.710
There are gifts in here for

35:15.710 --> 35:17.360
Mrs. Chen and the villagers.

35:18.030 --> 35:19.400
Didn't you want to donate books
to No.1 High School?

35:19.400 --> 35:20.280
Bring them here.

35:20.280 --> 35:21.140
I'll pack them.

35:21.320 --> 35:22.420
I ordered them at the bookstore.

35:22.420 --> 35:23.960
I asked them to deliver them.

35:23.960 --> 35:26.090
I'm not carrying anything that heavy.

35:27.260 --> 35:28.220
It is a bit much.

35:28.810 --> 35:30.230
But the post office is too slow.

35:30.230 --> 35:31.070
We might get home

35:31.070 --> 35:32.330
before the stuff does.

35:32.880 --> 35:33.680
In the future,

35:33.760 --> 35:36.020
what you send today can arrive tomorrow.

35:36.710 --> 35:38.630
You're kidding. How is that possible?

35:38.630 --> 35:39.830
How is it impossible?

35:39.840 --> 35:40.710
We should always have

35:40.710 --> 35:41.630
some dreams.

35:43.960 --> 35:44.440
Mom.

35:45.410 --> 35:47.370
Did you ask Granny Yu?

35:47.400 --> 35:48.330
What did she say?

35:49.150 --> 35:50.410
She hasn't agreed yet.

35:51.030 --> 35:52.480
She has to wait for her son.

35:52.480 --> 35:53.190
She hasn't left this house

35:53.190 --> 35:54.630
for over 10 years,

35:54.650 --> 35:55.980
and it's New Year's too.

35:56.670 --> 35:57.840
I can understand that.

35:57.840 --> 35:59.770
I'm just worried about her health.

36:00.510 --> 36:00.880
Okay,

36:00.880 --> 36:02.300
I'll go talk to the subdistrict committee.

36:02.300 --> 36:04.500
I'll ask them to check on her more often.

36:04.960 --> 36:06.880
Have you prepared the gifts
for Zhou Cheng's family?

36:06.880 --> 36:08.080
When do you plan to go?

36:09.480 --> 36:11.210
I'll discuss it with him again.

36:11.400 --> 36:11.760
Mom.

36:12.000 --> 36:13.960
You and Uncle go back first
the day after tomorrow.

36:13.960 --> 36:15.290
I'll go by myself later.

36:15.370 --> 36:16.900
No, let's go back together.

36:16.920 --> 36:18.250
A few days won't matter.

36:18.280 --> 36:19.320
We'll wait for you.

36:19.320 --> 36:20.880
Don't wait. I'm going out of town.

36:20.880 --> 36:21.550
Just pack.

36:22.280 --> 36:22.710
Okay.

36:27.480 --> 36:30.160
[Jingcheng]

36:48.550 --> 36:49.150
Comrade.

36:49.190 --> 36:50.230
It looks like it's going to snow.

36:50.230 --> 36:51.290
Are we still going?

37:37.920 --> 37:38.400
Sir.

37:38.840 --> 37:39.370
Let's go.

37:39.880 --> 37:41.080
To the train station.

37:41.110 --> 37:41.710
All right.

37:48.630 --> 37:49.760
I don't think this woman

37:49.760 --> 37:50.490
and the child

37:50.840 --> 37:52.300
are related to Zhou Cheng.

37:53.860 --> 37:54.550
But I'm still upset

37:54.550 --> 37:56.440
that he hid it from me.

37:59.030 --> 38:01.430
I don't want to
fall into a romantic cliché.

38:02.270 --> 38:04.270
I'll wait for him to tell me himself.

38:56.320 --> 38:58.450
The skin should be thick, not too thin.

38:59.290 --> 39:00.480
When you pinch it,

39:01.070 --> 39:02.400
don't do it too tightly.

39:05.190 --> 39:05.760
Look.

39:06.190 --> 39:08.000
Birdcage shape, grain beak.

39:08.190 --> 39:09.050
Pretty, right?

39:09.070 --> 39:10.760
It's so exquisite.

39:12.550 --> 39:13.070
Got it?

39:13.070 --> 39:13.550
Come on, wrap one.

39:13.550 --> 39:14.320
Let me try.

39:15.230 --> 39:15.760
Xiaolan.

39:16.280 --> 39:17.680
I'll make one for you too.

39:19.880 --> 39:20.410
Xiaolan.

39:20.800 --> 39:22.060
Why are you zoning out?

39:22.280 --> 39:23.030
Look at you.

39:23.230 --> 39:24.000
Zhou Cheng

39:24.000 --> 39:25.400
went back to the capital for New Year,

39:25.400 --> 39:27.130
and look at you,
you're already zoning out.

39:27.130 --> 39:28.770
You two
haven't even registered your marriage yet.

39:28.770 --> 39:30.190
Auntie, what are you saying?

39:30.190 --> 39:30.880
Tao is here.

39:32.280 --> 39:34.610
What were you guys talking about just now?

39:34.710 --> 39:36.040
I didn't hear anything.

39:36.800 --> 39:37.110
Okay.

39:37.110 --> 39:37.710
Good that you didn't hear it.

39:37.710 --> 39:38.510
I'll wrap one too.

39:38.510 --> 39:39.320
All right.

39:40.030 --> 39:40.710
Go play.

39:41.800 --> 39:43.060
We don't need you here.

39:44.000 --> 39:45.800
Fine, I'm being rejected again.

39:46.110 --> 39:47.040
Comrade Liu Fen.

39:47.550 --> 39:49.210
How did you convince Granny Yu

39:49.250 --> 39:50.250
to get her

39:50.280 --> 39:51.840
to come to our house for New Year?

39:51.840 --> 39:52.550
I was worried

39:52.550 --> 39:53.480
that after we all came back,

39:53.480 --> 39:54.510
what if when she was alone

39:54.510 --> 39:55.550
at home...

39:57.360 --> 39:59.590
Say auspicious things during New Year's.

39:59.590 --> 40:01.400
What do you mean you're worried about me?

40:01.400 --> 40:03.060
I'm the one worried about you.

40:04.080 --> 40:05.370
I'm worried your mom

40:05.400 --> 40:06.960
would get bullied by others.

40:06.960 --> 40:08.190
That's why I came.

40:08.590 --> 40:10.450
Otherwise, I wouldn't have come.

40:11.130 --> 40:11.670
That's great.

40:11.670 --> 40:14.600
Look at all this dried seafood.

40:14.630 --> 40:16.180
How do we prepare this?

40:16.840 --> 40:18.240
Isn't the head chef here?

40:18.590 --> 40:20.550
Granny Yu is knowledgeable.

40:20.800 --> 40:21.800
Things that fly in the sky,

40:21.800 --> 40:23.030
run on the ground, and swim in the sea—

40:23.030 --> 40:23.920
she knows them all.

40:23.920 --> 40:24.590
Right?

40:24.800 --> 40:26.550
Don't flatter me.

40:26.920 --> 40:28.050
Granny Yu, teach us.

40:28.440 --> 40:29.210
Abalone...

40:29.920 --> 40:31.800
It needs to be soaked in clean water.

40:31.800 --> 40:33.400
Change the water twice a day.

40:33.400 --> 40:35.000
I think it'll be ready to cook

40:35.000 --> 40:36.000
by New Year's Eve.

40:36.030 --> 40:36.480
I see.

40:36.550 --> 40:37.000
All right!

40:37.000 --> 40:38.460
I'll go get a basin of water

40:38.960 --> 40:40.420
to soak the abalone first.

40:42.800 --> 40:43.510
Xiaolan!

40:44.840 --> 40:45.710
Mrs. Chen!

40:45.800 --> 40:47.150
Happy New Year.

40:47.150 --> 40:49.280
You're getting more and more radiant.

40:49.880 --> 40:51.840
Is Chen Qing coming back this year?

40:52.440 --> 40:53.400
He can't.

40:53.680 --> 40:54.590
He insisted on going abroad

40:54.590 --> 40:55.920
for graduate school.

40:56.280 --> 40:57.230
We don't have to pay

40:57.230 --> 40:58.540
his tuition,

40:58.760 --> 41:00.590
but we have to pay for his travel.

41:00.840 --> 41:01.810
It's so far away.

41:01.840 --> 41:03.700
He can't just come back whenever.

41:03.970 --> 41:05.040
You're better.

41:05.070 --> 41:06.360
Staying by your mom's side—

41:06.360 --> 41:07.400
that's being a good daughter.

41:07.400 --> 41:07.960
No.

41:07.980 --> 41:09.240
Chen Qing is good, too.

41:09.280 --> 41:11.080
Mrs. Chen. Happy New Year.

41:11.110 --> 41:12.070
You're all back!

41:12.070 --> 41:13.320
Come, come, have a bite at my place.

41:13.320 --> 41:14.580
We're learning to make

41:14.600 --> 41:15.710
barbecue pork buns.

41:15.710 --> 41:17.110
The Cantonese love them.

41:17.110 --> 41:17.590
Come on.

41:17.670 --> 41:18.270
Oh, right.

41:18.360 --> 41:20.420
Look at the pastries I bought for you.

41:20.800 --> 41:22.130
I queued for a long time!

41:22.330 --> 41:23.360
You're too kind.

41:24.920 --> 41:25.760
Where's your mom?

41:25.760 --> 41:26.190
My mom?

41:26.370 --> 41:26.880
She's inside.

41:26.880 --> 41:27.680
She's inside.

41:28.800 --> 41:30.320
Great. Let me ask you something.

41:30.320 --> 41:31.630
Since you're back,

41:31.880 --> 41:33.550
and the house is renovated...

41:34.230 --> 41:35.280
It's the New Year.

41:35.630 --> 41:36.830
You'll definitely be

41:37.320 --> 41:38.510
visiting around the village, right?

41:38.510 --> 41:39.040
Yes, yes.

41:39.360 --> 41:40.590
If someone

41:41.480 --> 41:42.540
wants to introduce

41:43.400 --> 41:44.530
a partner to your mom

41:44.590 --> 41:45.790
and have her remarry,

41:46.230 --> 41:47.430
would you agree to it?

41:48.110 --> 41:49.670
Would I agree to it?

41:49.920 --> 41:51.320
It doesn't matter if I do.

41:51.630 --> 41:52.840
It's up to my mom.

41:53.510 --> 41:54.640
That's for sure!

41:54.960 --> 41:55.590
Mrs. Chen!

41:57.340 --> 41:58.500
Tao, say hello.

41:58.550 --> 41:59.510
Hello, Mrs. Chen.

41:59.510 --> 42:00.760
You've grown so tall.

42:01.320 --> 42:02.480
Come in and sit for a while.

42:02.480 --> 42:03.200
Come on in.

42:03.230 --> 42:04.860
Liu Fen, you're so beautiful.

42:04.860 --> 42:06.720
More beautiful than a butterfly.

42:07.370 --> 42:08.010
Well...

42:08.370 --> 42:09.370
I... I won't go in.

42:09.400 --> 42:10.710
Since all of you are home.

42:10.710 --> 42:11.910
Just ask for me, okay?

42:12.760 --> 42:14.070
I'll come another day.

42:14.560 --> 42:15.160
I'm off.

42:15.190 --> 42:15.920
Take care.

42:15.920 --> 42:16.630
Goodbye, Mrs. Chen.

42:16.630 --> 42:18.030
We'll visit you later!

42:20.450 --> 42:21.040
Fengmei,

42:21.070 --> 42:21.800
what was it?

42:22.800 --> 42:23.230
Tao.

42:23.510 --> 42:25.770
Go back to your room and do your homework.

42:25.840 --> 42:27.030
Forget homework. It's New Year's.

42:27.030 --> 42:29.230
Come soak the abalone with me. Let's go.

42:30.320 --> 42:31.320
Why did she leave?

42:31.400 --> 42:33.800
She didn't stay
for the barbecue pork buns?

42:34.230 --> 42:35.070
She...

42:35.760 --> 42:37.360
came to be a matchmaker.

42:37.670 --> 42:38.470
A matchmaker?

42:38.800 --> 42:39.670
For whom?

42:40.130 --> 42:41.650
For Fen.

42:43.030 --> 42:44.230
Fen, be honest,

42:44.670 --> 42:45.960
do you want to consider

42:46.110 --> 42:47.310
finding a companion?

42:47.710 --> 42:48.190
I...

42:48.330 --> 42:49.280
What kind of man do you want to find?

42:49.280 --> 42:50.760
I don't plan to look for anyone else.

42:50.760 --> 42:51.410
I'm not.

42:51.440 --> 42:51.840
I mean,

42:51.880 --> 42:54.230
why would she try to
matchmake at this point of time?

42:54.230 --> 42:55.170
It's the New Year.

42:55.170 --> 42:56.900
She's just testing the waters.

42:57.120 --> 42:58.150
Who knows how many more people

42:58.150 --> 42:59.800
will come knocking soon.

43:00.320 --> 43:01.510
You need to figure out

43:01.510 --> 43:02.570
how to deal with it.

43:03.630 --> 43:04.550
Come on.

43:04.960 --> 43:06.690
Let's make barbecue pork buns.

43:08.510 --> 43:09.400
Let's make buns.

43:09.400 --> 43:10.400
Let's get to it. Hurry up.

43:10.400 --> 43:11.840
Let's go inside and make buns.
